theorem P1_iUnion {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {ι : Sort _} {f : ι → Set X} :
    (∀ i, Topology.P1 (f i)) → Topology.P1 (⋃ i, f i) := by
  intro hP
  dsimp [Topology.P1] at hP ⊢
  intro x hx
  rcases mem_iUnion.mp hx with ⟨i, hxfi⟩
  have hx_cl : x ∈ closure (interior (f i)) := (hP i) hxfi
  have h_subset : closure (interior (f i)) ⊆ closure (interior (⋃ j, f j)) := by
    have h_int : interior (f i) ⊆ interior (⋃ j, f j) := by
      have h_union : (f i : Set X) ⊆ ⋃ j, f j := by
        intro y hy
        exact mem_iUnion.mpr ⟨i, hy⟩
      exact interior_mono h_union
    exact closure_mono h_int
  exact h_subset hx_cl

theorem univ_has_all_Ps {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] :
    Topology.P1 (Set.univ : Set X) ∧ Topology.P2 (Set.univ : Set X) ∧ Topology.P3 (Set.univ : Set X) := by
  have hOpen : IsOpen (Set.univ : Set X) := isOpen_univ
  exact Topology.isOpen_has_all_Ps (X := X) (A := (Set.univ : Set X)) hOpen
